data.description:
LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION! Conveniently located just minutes from I95, I295, Fort Lee & the Meadowville Technology Park, Amazon Fullfilment and the LEGO factory.
This 3Br 1 Ba Rancher on a large corner lot with a fenced in back yard and plenty of privacy is the perfect starter home or even empty nesters!
Rear patio with awning, 2 car driveway and street parking, 2 storages sheds with electricity both convey as is.
Oversized laundry room has the potential to add on a half bath.
LVP Floors, Dishwasher, water heater, HVAC unit, & panel box all less than 5 years old. Roof is less than 10 years old.
This home is being sold as-is.
Schedule your showing today!
Owner/Agent
